{"tid":25764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武前線創辦人畀人要脅公開個人資料","createTime":"2016-12-06T10:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:56:50.000Z","uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18c6aa35b76f82875465ed31b5b081e8c02f36c","tid":25764,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F636620766542560&d=UpCGnSyyXP1JUvkUpR2X9QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f00bb503\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560</a><br />\n<br />\n自從將騎劫事件還原並公諸於世之後，本來屬於我地&amp;#22021;專頁成為騎劫者龐大&amp;#22021;輿論機器，用無稽之談之聲明，去抹黑我地。無奈&amp;#22021;係，我地始終一直處於弱勢，後備專頁所得&amp;#22021;迴響亦唔夠騎劫者大。我&amp;#21707;&amp;#21946;Facebook，&amp;#21946;節目公開張善健篤灰等佢地所做&amp;#22021;惡行。現時換來&amp;#22021;係，騎劫者欲重施故技，要脅公開我地兩個個人資料。&amp;#21946;我地仲有勇氣去出呢篇文時，兩位創辦人個人資料隨時滿天飛，希望大家能夠幫一個忙，將我地一直以來所面對&amp;#22021;事分享開去，令大家知道而家已被騎劫&amp;#22021;專頁係幾咁危險，更多人知道佢地&amp;#22021;惡行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hlnt08gz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhlnt08gz&h=064b9f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2l5qxbon\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2l5qxbon&h=114750f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經有人&amp;#25598;到要脅爆人資料條友電話係63116411<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n76wd8bj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn76wd8bj&h=a76cd924&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34d2197f85fa8de32ce165631935d5999243aa36","tid":25764,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:23:38.000Z","msg":"勇武前線創辦人畀人要脅公開個人資料<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvaliantfrontier%2Fposts%2F636620766542560&d=UpCGnSyyXP1JUvkUpR2X9QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f00bb503\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/valiantfrontier/posts/636620766542560</a><br />\n自從將騎劫事件還原並公諸於世之後，本來屬於我地嘅專頁成為騎劫者龐大嘅輿論機器，用無稽之談之聲明，去抹黑我地。無奈嘅係，我地始終一直處於弱勢，後備專頁所得嘅迴響亦唔夠騎劫者大。我哋喺Facebook，喺節目公開張善健篤灰等佢地所做嘅惡行。現時換來嘅係，騎劫者欲重施故技，要脅公開我地兩個個人資料。喺我地仲有勇氣去出呢篇文時，兩位創辦人個人資料隨時滿天飛，希望大家能夠幫一個忙，將我地一直以來所面對嘅事分享開去，令大家知道而家已被騎劫嘅專頁係幾咁危險，更多人知道佢地嘅惡行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hlnt08gz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhlnt08gz&h=064b9f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2l5qxbon\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2l5qxbon&h=114750f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經有人揾到要脅爆人資料條友電話係63116411<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n76wd8bj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn76wd8bj&h=a76cd924&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"e86a7f7770daa55e2f8b88dfbed5add7610c2275","tid":25764,"uid":6818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e5738a93380a4116590da7e49fc67b2c627c1f","tid":25764,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣可以幫到巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd779fe8f82bf10cd1ce3c6a025baa5a60b6f210","tid":25764,"uid":33880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f622d1ab4ef226e800deca2a2e30fb6fac86c0","tid":25764,"uid":33